{"word":"G5035 - ταχύ - tachý - takh-oo' - Lightly","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ταχύ</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">tachý</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">takh-oo'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Lightly</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"தீவிரமான - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"quickly, speedily"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Neuter singular of <a href=\"#/G5036 - ταχύς - tachýs - takh-oos'/5036\">G5036</a> (as adverb); <i>shortly</i>, that is, <i>without delay</i>, <i>soon</i>, or (by surprise) <i>suddenly</i>, or (by implication of ease) <i>readily:</i> - lightly, quickly.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}